description:
Conquer the biggest, toughest jobs with Glad Project Pro Extra Trash Bags. These extra large trash bags are designed so that you can fill it, or stuff it with just about anything including construction debris. These 45 gallon capacity black contractor bags are made extra strong and can hold up to 200 pounds. The 3 mil thickness provides maximum strength to withstand punctures and tears. The flap tie closure makes sealing and carrying the load easy and dependable. These extra large trash bags are ideal for debris from cleaning up after a demolition to disposing of major yard waste. You can count on Glad bags to contain your messiest trash.

Usage Directions: Cross tie the four flaps, grab bag by the knot and remove from container. Toss the secure bag into the garbage.

Caution Statements: Plastic bags can be dangerous. To avoid danger of suffocation, keep all plastic bags away from babies and children. DO NOT USE FOR FOOD STORAGE.
